{"questionId":"25845","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider the function&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></msup></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℝ</mi></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>g</mi></math> is given by&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>, where&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℝ</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≠</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≠</mo><mn>3</mn></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Solve the inequality&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>≥</mo><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt to find at least one intersection point&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>26686</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>177935</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>06167</mn><mo>…</mo></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>27</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>178</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>06<